narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Greater understanding of neighborhoods literature as it relates to education and housing. Gained preliminary understanding of R language.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Strengths: structure (freedom to select 3 reading memos over the semester instead of assigned reading memos/weekly); Weaknesses: just one - I didn't particularly like having to present the final project twice.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would highly recommend to a student interested in neighborhood effects literature and critical thinking!
